fields.title: Billing website
fields.description: This website was one of my very first that I built completely with my own logic without following any tutorials. This website allows the users to perform billing. Its algorithm precisely sums up the information and presents it. It can be used in any retail stores for hassle free billing. Its simple UI and vast functionalities makes it a great choice for the many small and medum size retail outlets.

fields.title: The Wireless - News website
fields.description: The Wireless is a website that provides the user with national news of various topics. The website is built using ReactJS for the fontEnd and the reliable News API is used to fetch fresh and reliable news

fields.title: BlogShare
fields.description: BlogShare is a seamless and powerful webapp that allows people to share anything and everything. It is a great platform for people to read and share anything that they want to. The powerful technologies of ReactJS and Django are used to build the frontend and backend respectively.

fields.title: Food recipe App
fields.built_with: HTML, CSS, JavaScript and ThemeAldb API
fields.description: This website suggests the user the best dishes they can make with an ingredient they have at their disposal. This website uses vanilla HTML, CSS and JavaScript. It fetches the data from ThemeAldb API.

fields.title: Dino Runner Game
fields.description: This is the classic Chrome dino runner game. I built it to understand the concepts such as eventlisteners, background looping, collision, translate and so on.

fields.title: Calm (Clone)
fields.description: It is a simple UI that I created to learn how to make stunning looking hero landing pages. Calm uses simple HTML and CSS.

fields.title: Four Seasons - Hualalai (Clone)
fields.description: It is a simple clone of the landing page of Four Seasons resort. I created it to understand the design of a professional and creative website.

fields.title: E-commerce Website
fields.description: An E-commerce website with paypal payment integration. Products can be displayed for sale. Users can browse through the products, order them, write reviews, rate the product and so on.

fields.title: The Notes App
fields.description: A notes app that I created to cement the concepts of Create, Read, Update and Delete functions. It allows the user to create a note, update it and delete it whenever necessary.
